cara menghadapi temu duga.

1035
00:41:44,159 --> 00:41:45,080
Baguslah begitu!

1036
00:41:48,679 --> 00:41:49,199
Mari.

1037
00:41:49,799 --> 00:41:50,600
Semoga awak berjaya.

1038
